{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_72","type":"agent_message","text":"The first fix removed the original top-level AOT initializer failure, but two native-only issues remain: Spring still needs AOT mappings for the nested `TestClassScannerTest` class template case, and the explicit classpath-scan assertion now fails because native mode scans the built executable path rather than the JVM test classes directory. I’m inspecting Spring’s `TestClassScanner` behavior next to decide whether this stays a metadata fix or whether the `7.0.0` test itself has to be narrowed for native mode."}}
